1. *Gospodara* nema kod kuće. (The master is not at home.)
2. U posljednje vrijeme *gospodar* ima problema sa zdravljem. (Lately, the master has been having health problems.)
3. Naš *gospodar* je jako strog, ali pravedan. (Our master is very strict, but fair.)
4. *Gospodaru*, treba li da pripremimo večeru? (Master, should we prepare dinner?)
5. Nije pristojno prekinuti *gospodara* dok govori. (It's not polite to interrupt the master while he's speaking.)
6. *Gospodar* se vratio kući kasno sinoć. (The master came home late last night.)
7. Radnici su se žalili na *gospodarevu* pohlepu. (The workers complained about the master's greed.)
8. Naš se *gospodar* uvijek oblači u skladu sa svojim položajem. (Our master always dresses in accordance with his position.)
9. *Gospodarima* je bilo teško zadržati posjede nakon propasti carstva. (It was difficult for the masters to retain their estates after the empire's collapse.)
10. *Gospodaru*, hoćete li nešto popiti? (Master, would you like something to drink?)